# Vulnerabilities in Go modules vendored inside upstream release binaries we
# download as-is (kubectl, terraform). A fix exists in the Go module itself,
# but no kubectl/terraform release has been cut yet that picks it up, so
# there is nothing in this repo to bump. Re-evaluate this list whenever
# KUBECTL_VERSION or TERRAFORM_VERSION changes and drop any CVE that's
# resolved in the new release.

# kubectl v1.36.2 - golang.org/x/net / stdlib
CVE-2026-25681
CVE-2026-27136
CVE-2026-33814
CVE-2026-39821
CVE-2026-39822

# terraform v1.15.8 - stdlib
CVE-2026-27145
CVE-2026-42504
